{
  "stem": "1641.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Everybody got about half a bread, which was maybe-- maybe 750 grams of bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And everybody, as far as I can tell, got one tin, just like a Campbell's soup, a soup with some meat in it, some beef pieces.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That was the provision of food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So we could put it in our pocket, the bread here, and half a bread here, half a bread there, and the meat in the middle.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "March, big march.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Five in a row, and we marched out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That was early in the morning, 5 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we marched and marched, marched all day long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And by the time we got into late afternoon, we-- we started to find the first bodies on the roadside, people who couldn't march fast enough in the previous group, people who sat down near a tree, to just lean against a tree [? to find ?] a little rest, they all shot through the head.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Later on I could-- we saw all the bodies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But later on, we could actually see all the-- a Jewish man sitting on the roadside, and an SS man stops his BMW motorbike, and walks up to him.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And the Jewish man is doing, please, please.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I get up in a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I just have a little rest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Shot him, shot him through the chest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they shot, every-- every few seconds somebody got shot, here or there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Somebody who sat down in the middle of the road, of course, got shot right away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "You couldn't stop for one second.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "If you're stopped for more than two seconds, you got shot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And in front of us went a big group of girls, many young women.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And there you could see, first you could see the bloody tampons lying everywhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
